WEBVTT

00:10:27.561 --> 00:10:30.133
So, how do we begin to dismantle rigidity

00:10:30.157 --> 00:10:32.157
and embrace emotional agility?

00:10:33.791 --> 00:10:35.450
As that young schoolgirl,

00:10:35.474 --> 00:10:38.841
when I leaned into those blank pages,

00:10:38.865 --> 00:10:41.254
I started to do away with feelings

00:10:41.278 --> 00:10:44.396
of what I should be experiencing.

00:10:45.254 --> 00:10:48.600
And instead started to open my heart
to what I did feel.

00:10:49.103 --> 00:10:50.290
Pain.

00:10:50.679 --> 00:10:51.829
And grief.

00:10:52.838 --> 00:10:54.377
And loss.

00:10:54.401 --> 00:10:55.551
And regret.

00:10:57.972 --> 00:11:00.553
Research now shows